originalText:
::An unusually muscular boulder of a woman takes a firm stand before you while wielding a massive sledgehammer. She doesn't seem very pleased, and her rock-shattering stare seems equally as potent as her strong arms. Also, the giant hammer in her hands looks like it has connected with quite a number of skulls in the past, further contributing to the whole image.::

You filthy male pig! You are all bastards, bre, cheaters, selfish good-for-nothings! Like that husband of mine, the love of my life, Stjepanicije, who cheated on me with some, some Svetlana girl! Uh, bre!
